text: The Upthrown Stone () is a 1969 Hungarian drama movie directed by Sándor Sára and starring Lajos Balázsovits, Todor Todorov, László Bánhidi, István Iglódi, Tibor Molnár, Katalin Berek, Ferenc Némethy. ==Other websites== * Category:1969 drama movies Category:Hungarian movies Category:Movies directed by Sándor Sára
title: The Upthrown Stone
